   <content type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;utcg-blender-violin-workshop&quot;&gt;UTCG Blender Violin Workshop&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here’s the recording for Part 1 of UTCG’s Blender Workshop on October 22, 2021.&lt;/p&gt;

